  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IDLE GAME</h2><br>An idle game is a game where you play by \"not playing\"... the way the game works.. is that you let your character farming resources.<br>and leveling up.. and then you buy the upgrades.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why make this?</h2><br>Idle games are very small games wich allows you learn how to play the game quickly..<br>Many players enjoy this format of gaming. wich allows them to work or watch tv while playing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588500/extras/abfa1b16f5e4066c27a22ff943eaf352.webp?t=1751659133\" width=558 height=61 /></span><br><br>Autocraft is a game where you will be playing as a mighty champion that can collect loot.. as well as enchant his shield with bonus gems found around.<br><br>Btw this is like my previous games! If you liked them go ahead!! If you didnt please skip!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588500/extras/0edf663dde1362eccd8a81108952b2e0.webp?t=1751659133\" width=558 height=61 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shield socketing<br></li><li>Gear looting<br></li><li>Jewels purchases<br></li><li>Auto-Battle<br></li><li>Study new skills<br></li><li>Buy some pots</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IDLE GAME</h2><br>An idle game is a game where you play by \"not playing\"... the way the game works.. is that you let your character farming resources.<br>and leveling up.. and then you buy the upgrades.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why make this?</h2><br>Idle games are very small games wich allows you learn how to play the game quickly..<br>Many players enjoy this format of gaming. wich allows them to work or watch tv while playing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588500/extras/abfa1b16f5e4066c27a22ff943eaf352.webp?t=1751659133\" width=558 height=61 /></span><br><br>Autocraft is a game where you will be playing as a mighty champion that can collect loot.. as well as enchant his shield with bonus gems found around.<br><br>Btw this is like my previous games! If you liked them go ahead!! If you didnt please skip!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2588500/extras/0edf663dde1362eccd8a81108952b2e0.webp?t=1751659133\" width=558 height=61 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shield socketing<br></li><li>Gear looting<br></li><li>Jewels purchases<br></li><li>Auto-Battle<br></li><li>Study new skills<br></li><li>Buy some pots</li></ul>",
